    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
      <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8;">Seaena Consulting was founded on a simple principle: <strong>Strategy + Execution.</strong></p>

      <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8;">After years leading growth initiatives at Fortune 500 companies and high-growth startups, Louis and Rob recognized a gap in the consulting market. Traditional firms deliver strategic recommendations but leave execution to chance. Boutique consultants focus on tactics without strategic vision.</p>

      <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8;">We left our corporate roles to build something different—a consulting practice that combines enterprise-grade strategic frameworks with hands-on execution support. Every engagement is founder-led. Every recommendation is implementation-ready.</p>

      <h3 class="mt-3">Our Mission</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.8;">Make enterprise growth predictable and sustainable. We believe scaling a business shouldn't be a series of educated guesses. With the right methodology, data-driven insights, and execution discipline, growth becomes systematic.</p>
